<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.5.8">
<l>kēvala maṉṟuka ṭaliṉōcai kēṇmiṉka ḷāyaṉkai  yāmpalvanteṉ</l>
<l>āviya ḷavuma ṇaintuniṟku maṉṟiyu maintuka ṇaiterintiṭ</l>
<l>ṭēvalaṅ kāṭṭivi vaṉoruva ṉippaṭi yēpukun teytiṭāmuṉ</l>
<l>kōvalar kūttaṉku ṟippaṟintu kuṟuṅkuṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sound of the sea is not alone. Listen!</l>
<l rend="indent">The bamboo [flute] in the herder’s hands,</l>
<l>Coming and snuffing out my whole soul, persists. Besides, before that one,</l>
<l>Revealing his five [flower] arrows, displaying his archery skills,</l>
<l rend="indent">can come this way and shoot [me],</l>
<l>Knowing the intentions of the cowherd dancer,</l>
<l rend="indent">make sure you take me to Kuṟuṅkuṭi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
